# Online Course Progress Tracker

## Description
This project is a ReactJS-based web application that helps users track course progress, manage learning goals, and monitor achievements.

## Features
- Dashboard with course progress
- Weekly progress charts
- Learning streak tracker
- Achievement badges
- Course deadlines
- Study timer
- Course search functionality
- Notes management
- Download progress report
- User profile management
- Course ratings
- Learning goal tracker
- Dark mode support
- API integration

## Technologies Used
- ReactJS
- JavaScript
- HTML
- CSS
- Context API
- Recharts
- localStorage
- REST API
